
-- DHOOM: Query Catalogue --
queries{id, join_tier, name, notes, operation, predicate, tpch}:
Q6, 1, Forecasting Revenue Change, "Pure LINEITEM scan, no join. Validates sequential storage + filter throughput.", filter + scan aggregate, "shipdate in [1994-01-01, 1995-01-01), discount in [0.05,0.07], qty < 24", 6
Q1, 2, Pricing Summary Report, "Groups by (returnflag, linestatus). Validates HashMap aggregation over 6M rows.", filter + group_by + multi-aggregate, shipdate <= 1998-12-01, 1
Q14, 1, Promotion Effect, Pullback join LINEITEM->PART. promo_revenue = 100 * sum(promo_price) / sum(total_price). Validates correctness of join + conditional agg., filter + pullback_join + conditional aggregate, "shipdate in [1995-09-01, 1995-10-01), join PART on p_type LIKE PROMO%", 14
Q3, 2, Shipping Priority, Bitmap index on customer segment pre-filters ~30K BUILDING customers before any row scan. Demonstrates predicate pushdown efficiency., CUSTOMER-bitmap -> ORDERS -> LINEITEM 3-way join + aggregate, "c_mktsegment = BUILDING, o_orderdate < 1995-03-15, l_shipdate > 1995-03-15", 3


