-- DHOOM: Storage Geometry --
storage_geometry{implication, reason, table, mode|sequential}:
O(1) point lookup by row id. Full scan is cache-linear., "l_id is auto-increment dense int (K=0 base). BaseGeometry::Flat with step=1.", LINEITEM
O(1) point lookup by orderkey. Q3 bitmap join resolves orderkeys in O(|BUILDING_customers|) not O(|ORDERS|)., "o_orderkey is sparse (gaps 1-8 between keys). BundleStore::new() auto-selects HashMap.", ORDERS, :hashed
Bitmap over mktsegment builds in O(150K). Q3 segment filter costs O(150K) not O(1.5M orders)., c_custkey is dense 1..150000., CUSTOMER

